                  li: a(href="https://apkpro.ru/upload/docs/tsos/%D0%9A%D0%BE%D0%BD%D1%82%D0%B5%D0%BD%D1%82_%D0%98%D0%BD%D1%84%D0%BE%D1%80%D0%BC%D0%B0%D1%86%D0%B8%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BD%D1%8B%D0%B5%20%D0%BC%D0%B0%D1%82%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B8%D0%B0%D0%BB%D1%8B%20%D0%B4%D0%BB%D1%8F%20%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%B8%D1%82%D0%B5%D0%BB%D0%B5%D0%B9.pdf" target="_blank") для родителей

